flowRoot.flowPara: Add Red Hat symbols to your diagram:
Press Ctrl-Shift-Y to bring up the symbols panel. From this view, you can drag the required symbols into your diagram.
Use the official Red Hat colors:
At the bottom of your Inkscape window, you will find the color palette, showing the available colors to use in your diagram.
At the far right of the palette, click the '<' symbol to bring up a list of available palettes. Select Red Hat diagram colors.
You will notice that the available colors have now changed. Use these colors in your graphic elements.
